item.title: CI Analytics
item.description: Introduction CI Analytics is a feature of LocalStack Web Application that allows users to get insights into their CI builds. CI Analytics unifies additional features, such as Cloud Pods & Stack Insights, and augments them with an integrated view of CI builds to provide users with insights and facilitate debugging. The features include: CI Project Runs: Offers a unified view of all CI builds for a particular project. Log Output: Enables viewing of detailed logs for individual CI builds.
